{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_08_03",
  "title": "小美山愛",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "――よし、そこまでだ。愛、休んでくれ\nそれ以上のトレーニングは負荷が増え過ぎる",
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……。はい、ありがとうございました！",
      "startTime": 6.952448972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブは明日だ\n衣装を直すかどうかの判断は、今日がタイムリミットだ",
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もし衣装が着られなかったら、大急ぎで直してもらう\n……いいな？",
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "その時は……仕方ありません",
      "startTime": 24.1817448457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もしそうなったら\n私のアイドルとしてのプライドはボロボロです……",
      "startTime": 31.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "これだけ頑張ったんだ。きっと成果は出ているさ",
      "startTime": 36.101539747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだと、いいんですけど……",
      "startTime": 40.1382064422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。試着の前に体重をはかってみないか？",
      "startTime": 43.8315390986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、怖いです……\nもし、痩せてなかったら……どうしよう……",
      "startTime": 49.9040555955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫。勇気を出して",
      "startTime": 53.8269131741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃ、{user}さんからお先にどうぞ",
      "startTime": 56.5962782702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺の体重をはかってどうするんだ……\nさあ、自分を信じて。あれだけ腹筋したじゃないか",
      "startTime": 63.199998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……あっ、{user}さん\n覗かないで下さい！　恥ずかしいです！",
      "startTime": 71.7154399397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめん、覗くつもりは……\nあっ、電話だ。ちょっと待ってくれ",
      "startTime": 78.5666650136,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2572.522051800007,
          "startTime": 78.0333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5429.647095700006,
          "startTime": 80.8904583772
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8286.772139600003,
          "startTime": 83.7475834211
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9372.522051800004,
          "startTime": 84.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "もう、ごまかさないで下さい～！",
      "startTime": 81.8271606925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "はい、もしもし、お世話になっておりま……え？\nサイズを……？　それは本当なんですか？",
      "startTime": 89.8264097402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんですか？　一体誰から……",
      "startTime": 94.3202194534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、早急に対応をお願いします！　ではまた後で\n……愛、喜んでくれ。誤解だったよ",
      "startTime": 103.7113871994,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4406.445197700009,
          "startTime": 102.6133312988
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "誤解って、何がですか？",
      "startTime": 108.0472719832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "今のは、ステージ衣装を作ってくれた会社からの電話だ",
      "startTime": 111.1538706306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "どうやら、愛の衣装だけサイズを間違えて\nウエストを細く作ってしまったらしい",
      "startTime": 118.1666629791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "ええーっ！？　それじゃあ私\n太った訳じゃなかったんですね！",
      "startTime": 123.3406299275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "どうりでおかしいと思った……\n愛の見た目は変わっていなかったし",
      "startTime": 128.7666629791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……\n私、ベストの状態でステージに立てるんですね！",
      "startTime": 134.2251647951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "これでリズノワのみんなにも、ミクちゃんにも\n迷惑を掛けなくて済みます",
      "startTime": 143.0251647951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "衣装はすぐに直してくれるそうだ\nギリギリ明日のライブに間に合いそうで良かった",
      "startTime": 148.2666629791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、じゃあこの衣装はお直しを……\n……あっ、待って下さい",
      "startTime": 155.387522952,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7699.999999999989,
          "startTime": 163.087522952
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "私、確認したいことがあるのでちょっと失礼します！",
      "startTime": 157.9715805375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしました！\n見て下さい、{user}さん！",
      "startTime": 168.787522952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "とても良く似合ってるけど、よく着られたな\nサイズもピッタリじゃないか。……もしかして",
      "startTime": 175.3727270849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、その通りです！　ダイエットのおかげで\nこのサイズでも着られるようになりました！",
      "startTime": 183.8966839792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "だから、衣装は直してもらわなくて大丈夫です",
      "startTime": 187.1966305895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "結果的に、愛はますますスタイルが良くなって解決か\n一時はどうなるかと思ったけど……努力の成果だな",
      "startTime": 195.9666629791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "明日のステージ、期待してるぞ",
      "startTime": 200.1492832823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　さらに身軽になった、軽快なダンスを\nファンのみなさんに観てもらいます！",
      "startTime": 207.1666629791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "startTime": 210.135096121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_circularstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 211.5684294543
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_circularstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 211.5684294543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_03-ai020.m4a",
